#. <section class="sutta" id="sn13.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn13.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 13"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 13"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn13.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Abhisamayavagga"
msgstr "1. Comprehension"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn13.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Dutiyapabbatasutta"
msgstr "10. A Mountain (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn13.10:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, himavā pabbatarājā parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ "
"gaccheyya, ṭhapetvā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose the Himalayas, the king of mountains, was worn away and "
"eroded except for seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds."

msgctxt "sn13.10:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn13.10:1.4"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yaṃ vā himavato pabbatarājassa parikkhīṇaṃ "
"pariyādiṇṇaṃ yā vā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā avasiṭṭhā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the portion of the Himalayas, the king of mountains, that has "
"been worn away and eroded, or the seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds "
"that are left?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.10:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ himavato pabbatarājassa yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ "
"pariyādiṇṇaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the portion of the Himalayas, the king of mountains, that has been "
"worn away and eroded is certainly more."

msgctxt "sn13.10:2.2"
msgid "appamattikā satta sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā avasiṭṭhā."
msgstr "The seven pebbles the size of mustard seeds are tiny."

msgctxt "sn13.10:2.3"
msgid ""
"Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upenti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ "
"upenti himavato pabbatarājassa parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ upanidhāya satta "
"sāsapamattiyo pāsāṇasakkharā avasiṭṭhā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the Himalayas, it’s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a "
"hundred thousandth part.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn13.10:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa diṭṭhisampannassa puggalassa "
"abhisametāvino etadeva bahutaraṃ dukkhaṃ yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, for a noble disciple accomplished in view, a person with "
"comprehension, the suffering that’s over and done with is more,"

msgctxt "sn13.10:3.2"
msgid "appamattakaṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr "what’s left is tiny."

msgctxt "sn13.10:3.3"
msgid ""
"Neva satimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na sahassimaṃ kalaṃ upeti na satasahassimaṃ kalaṃ "
"upeti purimaṃ dukkhakkhandhaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādiṇṇaṃ upanidhāya yadidaṃ "
"sattakkhattuṃparamatā."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the mass of suffering in the past that’s over and done with, it’"
"s not nearly a hundredth, a thousandth, or a hundred thousandth part, since "
"there are at most seven more lives."

msgctxt "sn13.10:3.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ mahatthiyo kho, bhikkhave, dhammābhisamayo, evaṃ mahatthiyo "
"dhammacakkhupaṭilābho”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how very beneficial it is to comprehend the teaching and gain the "
"vision of the teaching.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn13.10:3.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
